Function: pollegendre
Section: polynomials
C-Name: pollegendre
Prototype: LDn
Help: pollegendre(n,{v=x}): legendre polynomial of degree n (n C-integer),
 in variable v
Doc: creates the $n^{\text{th}}$ \idx{Legendre polynomial}, in variable $v$.
 
 \syn{pollegendre}{n, v}, where $n$ and $v$ are \kbd{long}s and an omitted $v$
 is coded as $-1$.

